                      "content": "About the Role",
                      "fontFamily": "EB Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "HkGQY",
                      "name": "aboutText",
                      "fill": "$burgundy-80",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "We're looking for a curious and driven intern to join our Management team. In this role, you'll work directly with leadership on strategic initiatives that shape the future of conscious commerce.\n\nYou'll help coordinate cross-functional projects, conduct market research, and contribute to building internal processes that scale. This is a hands-on opportunity to learn how a purpose-driven startup operates from the inside.",
